    <p>
      goto certificates.mot-mobility.com
    </p>
    <p>
      button Request a Personal Certificate
    </p>
    <p>
      Install this certificate
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      back up the certificate in Firefox as .p12
    </p>
    <p>
      openssl pkcs12 -in DE01DSAPKC01A.p12 -out temp.pem
    </p>
    <p>
      openssl pkcs12 -in temp.pem -export -name &quot;Repackaged PKCS#12 file&quot; -out workaround.p12
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      use workaround.p12 in Private Key
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      The user name SHOULD BE DSA\a22543
    </p>
  </body>
